Description_lang: Rejuvenation instantly heals your target for $s1% of its total periodic effect and Regrowth's duration is increased by ${$s2/1000} sec.

description_blz.en_US: Rejuvenation instantly heals your target for 20% of its total periodic effect and Regrowth's duration is increased by 3 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Rejuvenecimiento sana al instante a tu objetivo un 20% de su efecto periódico total, y la duración de Recrecimiento aumenta 3 s.
description_blz.pt_BR: Rejuvenescer cura o alvo instantaneamente em 20% do efeito periódico total, e a duração de Recrescimento aumenta em 3 s.
description_blz.de_DE: Der Zauber 'Verjüngung' heilt Euer Ziel sofort um 20% seines gesamten regelmäßigen Effekts, und die Dauer von 'Nachwachsen' wird um 3 Sek. verlängert.
description_blz.en_GB: Rejuvenation instantly heals your target for 20% of its total periodic effect and Regrowth's duration is increased by 3 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Rejuvenecimiento sana al instante un 20% de su efecto periódico total, y la duración de Recrecimiento aumenta 3 s.
description_blz.fr_FR: Récupération rend instantanément à la cible un montant de points de vie égal à 20 % de son effet périodique total et la durée de Rétablissement est augmentée de 3 s.
description_blz.it_IT: Rinvigorimento cura istantaneamente il bersaglio del 20% delle cure fornite dal suo effetto periodico. Aumenta la durata di Ricrescita di 3 s.
description_blz.ru_RU: "Омоложение" мгновенно восполняет цели здоровье в объеме 20% своего периодического эффекта. "Восстановление" действует на 3 сек. дольше.
description_blz.ko_KR: 회복 시전 시 대상을 즉시 총 주기적인 치유량의 20%만큼 치유합니다. 또한 재생의 지속시간이 3초만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 回春術立刻使目標恢復相當於其總週期性效果20%的生命力，且癒合的持續時間延長3秒。
description_blz.zh_CN: 回春术立即为你的目标恢复其周期性效果总量20%的生命值，愈合的持续时间延长3秒。
